history.content:
Hello everyone!

 

HKN is hosting a Course Planning Session this Wednesday (4/15) from 5PM to 7PM online! https://berkeley.zoom.us/j/127660879

 

If you’re interested in receiving course planning advice from upperclassmen who have experience with the courses in different areas of EE and CS, this is just the event for you! 

 

At this event, volunteers will split into three large groups based on which field of EE or CS they’d like to talk about. You’ll have the chance to chat in small groups with them and gain insider info about the upper division courses available at Berkeley. We’ll switch groups often so that you can collect varied experiences, but if you’d like to just talk to people within your areas of interest, you’re welcome to do so as well.

 

If you’re interested, be sure to check it out! Hope to see you all there!

 https://www.facebook.com/events/660200874799478
